Class User

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
MailUser, OauthUser
@Entity
public class User
extends AuditModel
Object-oriented representation for table users

Base entity for specified types of users, using JOINED strategy for an inheritance

Storages: Users information

Logic: The base User class, linked with: Setting, Refresh, State. Contains user's name.
